description.en:
Royal BNB is a automatic reward generation token, holders of $RB token will automatically receive BNB rewards into their wallets every 30 minutes cycle, without the need to connect their wallet manually.

This is one of the most promising DeFi token with a 15% BNB reward offering, since launch the community and holders are growing at pace. A community driven enthusiasm and fantastic reward mechanism is being delivered to ensure the success of the token.
